  "prompt": "Which earphones are better under 2000?",
  "response": "When looking for earphones under \u20b92000, there are several good options available, depending on your preferences for sound quality, design, and features. Here are some popular and highly-rated earphones in this price range:\n\n---\n\n### **Best Wired Earphones Under \u20b92000**\n1. **Sony MDR-EX155AP**  \n   - Balanced sound with deep bass.  \n   - Lightweight and comfortable for long use.  \n   - Durable build quality.  \n\n2. **JBL C100SI**  \n   - Clear and punchy bass.  \n   - Tangle-free flat cable.  \n   - Affordable and reliable.  \n\n3. **Boat BassHeads 225**  \n   - Focus on bass-heavy sound.  \n   - Stylish design with tangle-free cable.  \n   - Affordable and widely popular.  \n\n4. **Sennheiser CX 180 Street II**  \n   - Crisp and clear audio with good bass.  \n   - Durable and ergonomic design.  \n   - Trusted brand for audio quality.  \n\n---\n\n### **Best Wireless Earphones Under \u20b92000**\n1. **Boat Airdopes 131**  \n   - Good sound quality with bass emphasis.  \n   - Compact design and decent battery life.  \n   - Affordable and reliable.  \n\n2. **realme Buds Wireless 2 Neo**  \n   - Balanced sound with good bass.  \n   - Neckband design with magnetic ear tips.  \n   - Lightweight and comfortable.  \n\n3. **pTron Bassbuds Pro**  \n   - Deep bass and clear audio.  \n   - IPX4 water resistance.  \n   - Long battery life with a compact charging case.  \n\n4. **Noise Buds VS104**  \n   - Decent sound quality with bass focus.  \n   - Stylish design and good battery life.  \n   - Affordable and reliable brand.  \n\n---\n\n### **Key Points to Consider**  \n- **Sound Signature**: Choose bass-heavy or balanced sound depending on your preference.  \n- **Comfort**: Ensure the earphones fit well for long listening sessions.  \n- **Build Quality**: Look for durable materials, especially in the cables or earbuds.  \n- **Battery Life (Wireless)**: Check for at least 10-15 hours of playback or more.  \n- **Brand Reputation**: Stick to trusted brands for better after-sales service and reliability.  \n\n---\n\nFor the best value, **Sony MDR-EX155AP** (wired) and **Boat Airdopes 131** (wireless) are excellent choices under \u20b92000.",
